column5: Plan on heading up tomorrow with my 16yr old  Any advice re fishing, launching etc.  Friend at work says there are some Musky in there.
sorry guys , I should have said Havelock, not Hastings.
I've never known it to be a great muskie lake, but it is good for small mouth and OK for walleye.  I used to use live frogs and catch fish all day.

lots of muskie  tonnes of largemouth and the walleye are with them  lots of smallies in certain areas  spinnerbaits baby 1 minus suspending thunderstick  this lake you will not get skunked always catch  fish on this one  watch out for the unmarked rock shoals by the trailer park
what he said been in there many times great little lake
